ns and social events for our graduate students our ethnic and cultural community centers across campus sponsor social and educational events that encourage cross disciplinary interactions please feel free to contact these centers for more information asian american activities center bechtel international center black community services center el centro chicano native american activities center woman's community center lesbian gay bisexual transgender center diversity in graduate education for additional information pleae contact roni holeton assistant dean for academic affairs at 650 721 3383 or roni stanford edu stanford university school of earth sciences 397 panama mall ca 94305 2210 mitchell building 101 tel 650 723 2544 2012 stanford university related resources employment opportunities hartley conference center health and safety computing resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
